:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 101110211: Config/Level/Mission/1011102/Act/Act101110211.json-->
:{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 378.ogg}} '''Serval:''' You see? Brothers and sisters need to have a scrap once in a while to get back on good terms.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: 101110211_loop1-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: 101110211_loop1-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Sorry for getting you involved in this.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201312002-->
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 379.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Agh, enough apologizing. My ears can't take any more.
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 380.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Honestly, this would have happened sooner or later. You just gave me an excuse to bring everything forward.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} So this is how brothers and sisters normally coexist?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201312005-->
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 381.ogg}} '''Serval:''' What's wrong with a bit of violent coexistence between siblings? Seems pretty normal to me.
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 382.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Hehe, I'm pulling your leg. Since I left the military, my brother and I have always steered clear of certain sensitive topics... Thinking about it, perhaps he's just been looking out for my feelings, shielding me all along.
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 383.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Knowing my temper, my brother almost certainly went to great lengths on many occasions for me. I should be thanking him.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Let the Stellaron hunt begin.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201312009-->
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 384.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Let's do this. I may never have come face to face with it, but this Stellaron cost me a nice, stable job. It's time to get even.
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 385.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Actually, I have another selfish motive... I want to prove to Cocolia that I was right. Once we've taken care of the Stellaron... maybe she'll go back to how she was.
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 386.ogg}} '''Serval:''' ...Sorry, hardly the time for me to be obsessing over all this.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} We've got this.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201312013-->
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 387.ogg}} '''Serval:''' As I mentioned, if we want to progress further north, we're gonna have to cross that "hell." Still, look at it this way: Just another arena to showcase our skills, right?
::{{A|VO chapter1 7 serval 388.ogg}} '''Serval:''' Now, if you're ready to get on stage, let's push for that standing ovation!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
